					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<div class="w-10 h-1 bg-accent mr-4"></div>
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary font-heading">PROFESSIONAL AC INSTALLATION</h2>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-darkgray mb-6">
						QUALITY INSTALLATION FOR LASTING COMFORT
					</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						When it comes to air conditioning installation, proper sizing, selection, and installation are crucial for
						optimal performance, efficiency, and longevity. At Alltek Services, our team of certified technicians has
						the expertise and experience to ensure your new AC system is installed correctly the first time.
					</p>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						We understand that investing in a new air conditioning system is a significant decision. That's why we take
						the time to assess your specific cooling needs, discuss your options, and help you select the right system
						for your home or business. We offer a range of energy-efficient options from leading manufacturers, ensuring
						you get the best value for your investment.
					</p>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-8">
						Our installation process is thorough and meticulous, with attention to every detail. From proper sizing and
						ductwork evaluation to final testing and system orientation, we ensure your new AC system is set up for
						optimal performance and efficiency.
					</p>
					<a
						href="/contact"
						class="inline-block bg-secondary hover:bg-secondary/90 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-md transition-colors"
					>
						Schedule a Consultation
					</a>
				</div>

				<div>
